title: Executive Order 8031-Revocation of Executive Order No. 4130 of January 22, 1925, Withdrawing Public Land for Fish Hatchery
content: By virtue of and pursuant to the authority vested in me by the act of June 25, 1910, ch. 421, 36 Stat. 847, Executive Order No. 4130 of January 22, 1925, withdrawing public land for use as a fish hatchery, is hereby revoked.
citation: Franklin D. Roosevelt, Executive Order 8031-Revocation of Executive Order No. 4130 of January 22, 1925, Withdrawing Public Land for Fish Hatchery Online by Gerhard Peters and John T. Woolley, The American Presidency Project https://www.presidency.ucsb.edu/node/371816
